      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters; any differences must be bounded by sensitivity analysis demonstrating negligible effect on NIH predictions.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency assessment was performed between the FDA benchmark pump experimental inputs (steady flow, water-glycerin, fixed RPM) and the VAD COU inputs (pulsatile flow, blood viscosity, variable RPM). The sensitivity of NIH predictions to these differences was not quantified. Achieved level 2 versus required level 4."
    }
